e:11px;color:rgba(238,240,255,0.22);line-height:1.6;'>Auto-generated by the <strong style='color:rgba(238,240,255,0.4);'>Aura Intake Assistant</strong>. This lead self-qualified through a multi-step briefing flow. <a href='YOUR_GOOGLE_SHEET_LINK' style='color:#6366f1;'>View in Google Sheets →</a></div></td></tr></table></body></html>",
        "options": {
          "attachmentsUi": {
            "attachmentsBinary": [
              { "property": "data" }
            ]
          }
        }
